description:
Ye Yu transmigrated into a self-cultivation novel.

Twice.

After her second transmigration, she became the evil female side lead of the novel.

In order to avoid a tragic ending, Ye Yu decided to stay away from the devil-like male lead. But she transmigrated over at an awkward time...

Therefore, the second day after Ye Yu transmigrated over, news spread in the devil world- The Demon King had just gotten married last night and got kicked out of the palace by the Devil Queen.

Demon officials: How bad must the Devil King's skills be?

Demon King: ...

After that-

Ye Yu said: Don’t come over! I am really not the female lead! Male lead, you have gotten the wrong person!>
